symc.name: HeapCompatibilityInformation_NOTE_standard_heap
symc.desc: The heap is a standard heap that does not support look-aside lists (pointer to a ULONG variable).

symc.name: HeapCompatibilityInformation_NOTE_supports_look_aside_lists

symc.name: HeapCompatibilityInformation_NOTE_lfh_enabled_heap
symc.desc: The low-fragmentation heap (LFH) has been enabled for the heap. Enabling the LFH disables look-aside lists (pointer to a ULONG variable).
